      • enrage

        public void enrage()
        Description copied from interface: Monster
        This method will double this.damage for this Monster if it hasn't already been enraged. In this case, this.isEnraged should be set to true. Otherwise, this method has no effect.

        This method will also display the message:

        "this.name has been enraged"
